title: Mets pitcher shows off the massive scary shark he just caught | For The Win
text:
Mets pitcher shows off the massive scary shark he just caught Mets pitcher shows off the massive scary shark he just caught By Luke Kerr-Dineen February 22, 2017 7:48 am Follow @LukeKerrDineen shares 
The good news about this for Mets fans is that Steven Matz will never again be nervous facing another batter. The dude caught a shark. And not just a shark. A really, big, massive shark. 
Seriously, look at this thing. Fishing with @BlacktipH was no joke. They got me and @GilmartinSean hooked up with some sharks! pic.twitter.com/ci8RYFcJ8i 
— Steven Matz (@Smatz88) February 21, 2017 
Look at it again. 
Eesh. Here’s a few GIFs of pandas to make it all better. More MLB!
